  <p>Join the <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#spine">#spine</a> group on irc.freenode.net.</p>
  <h3>The People who work on Spine</h3>
  <p> - Spine's author, <%= link_to "Alex MacCaw", "http://alexmaccaw.co.uk" %>, on <%= link_to "Twitter", "http://twitter.com/maccaw" %>.</p>
  <p> - A current maintaier, Aaron Eischeid, on <%= link_to "Twitter", "http://twitter.com/aeischeid" %>, on <%= link_to "Google+", "https://plus.google.com/112143844666155675269/" %>.</p>
  <p> - A current maintaier, Chris Engebretson, on <%= link_to "Google+", "https://plus.google.com/108878142598537707242/" %>.</p>
